data.description:
Seller will contribute up to 3% closing costs with good offer. Welcome to this exceptional 4/2.5 home nestled in a wonderful neighborhood in Mandarin, central to everything! This home is situated on a generous corner lot, this property boasts both space and style. One of the standout features of this home is the thoughtful expansion of the garage and addition of a guest bedroom above it, creating valuable extra square footage for your family's needs. 
Inside you will enjoy a large primary suite with an expansive closet that provides ample storage space, making it a dream come true for those with a passion for fashion!
Step outside to enjoy the spacious covered patio and fenced in backyard.
Minutes to great shopping and restaurants! Central to NS Mayport and NAS JAX..
